- cargroup = @booking.cargroup
- location = @booking.location
- outstanding = @booking.outstanding
%br/
Hi #{@user.name},
%br/
%br/
%br/
You've cancelled the following reservation:
%br/
%br/
%table{border: '0', cellpadding: '5', cellspacing: '0', style: "background:#eeeeee; font-size:12px; color:#333333;"}
	%tr
		%td Vehicle:
		%td
			%b #{cargroup.display_name}
	%tr
		%td Pick-up location: 
		%td
			%b #{location.name}
			= "("
			%a{href: "#{location.map_link}", target: "_blank"} View Map
			= ")"
	%tr
		%td Reservation begins: 
		%td
			%b #{@booking.starts.strftime("%d/%m/%y %I:%M %p")}
	%tr
		%td Reservation ends:
		%td
			%b #{@booking.ends.strftime("%d/%m/%y %I:%M %p")}
	%tr
		%td Reservation Confirmation Number:
		%td
			%b
				%a{href: "#{@booking.link}", target: "_blank"}
					= @booking.confirmation_key
%br/
%br/
%div{style: "background:#eeeeee; margin:0px; padding:10px; color:#000000;"}
	- if @charge
		%b
			Rs.
			= @charge.amount
		- if @charge.refund == 1
			is refunded back to the reservation.
		- else
			is added as cancellation charges to the reservation.
	- else
		%b
			No change in your reservation charges.
	%br/
	- if outstanding > 0
		You have
		%b
			Rs.
			#{outstanding}
		is outstanding against the reservation.
		- if @booking.starts < Time.now
			Please clear all your outstanding amount when you drop the vehicle back to Zoom.
		- else
			Please clear all your outstanding amount when you pick the vehicle from Zoom. Zoom reserve the right of cancelling the booking against any pending payment.
%br/
%br/
We're sorry that this reservation won't work out for you now, but check out what else is available for another time by logging onto
%b 
	%a{href: "http://www.zoomcar.in", target: "_blank"} www.zoomcar.in.
%br/
%br/
%br/
Happy Driving!
%br/
%br/ 
The Zoom Team
%br/
%br/
